        <item>
            <title>1.3.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 09:46:01 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.3.0</h2>
<p>New Work schedule: keep your Costco shifts and hours, see your weekly total, and paste your schedule to have Otto fill it in. Otto (including the local model) can now answer questions about when you work and how many hours you have.</p>
]]></description>
